text: The Kentuckian is a 1955 American western movie. It was directed by Burt Lancaster who also starred. Other actors included Dianne Foster, Diana Lynn, John McIntire, John Carradine, and John Litel. It was distributed by United Artists. ==Other websites== * * * * Category:1955 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies
